'''A Guide to Middle-Earth 2003 Calendar''' was published by Andrews McMeel Publishing and coincides with the book by [[Robert Foster]]. The calendar includes details ranging from [[Frodo Baggins]]' personality and genealogy to [[Sauron]]'s creation of the ring.

* ISBN 0-7407-2394-4
* 5⅜ x 5⅜ inches
* Shrink-wrapped
* Box
